Ingredient: red pepper flakes for garnish, or to taste
all-purpose flour, plus more for kneading
frozen chopped spinach - thawed, drained, and squeezed dry
cream cheese, cut into 1 inch cubes
pineapple cake mix (such as Duncan Hines® Pineapple Supreme)
confectioners' sugar for dusting, or as needed
skinless, boneless chicken breast halves - cut into 1/2-inch medallions
sea scallops, rinsed and patted dry
salt and freshly ground black pepper to taste
pecan shortbread cookies (such as Keebler Sandies), finely crushed
melted butter, or more as needed
warm water (110 degrees F/45 degrees C)
hot water, or more as needed (Optional)
red apple, cored and very thinly sliced
sweetened dried cranberries (such as Ocean Spray® Craisins®)
salt and black pepper, or to taste
frozen green peas, thawed and drained
